org.jtransfo

Class ReadOnlyDomainAutomaticTypeConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jtransfo.AbstractToDomainTypeConverter
      • org.jtransfo.ReadOnlyDomainAutomaticTypeConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Named, NeedsJTransfo, TypeConverter<Object,Object>

    public class ReadOnlyDomainAutomaticTypeConverter
extends AbstractToDomainTypeConverter
implements Named, NeedsJTransfo
    Type converter which only copies linked objects' fields to the transfer object. For converting transfer object to domain, the linked objects are looked up but the fields are not updated. This field automaticall detects if the field to convert is a list and uses ReadOnlyDomainAutomaticListTypeConverter in that case.
